dataset_id: Maps of Vegetation Types and Physiographic Features, Imnavait Creek, Alaska
title: Maps of Vegetation Types and Physiographic Features, Imnavait Creek, Alaska
summary: This dataset provides the spatial distribution of vegetation types, soil carbon, and physiographic features in the Imnavait Creek area, Alaska. Specific attributes include vegetation, percent water, glacial geology, soil carbon, a digital elevation model (DEM), surficial geology and surficial geomorphology. Data are also provided on the research grids for georeferencing. The map data are from a variety of sources and encompass the period 1970-06-01 to 2015-08-31.
